snippet.title: Kirby’s Blowout Blast – Nintendo 3DS Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Kirby is ready for action in a whole different dimension—the third dimension! Have a blast inhaling foes and blowing them away in 3D environments across 25+ stages.

Kirby’s Blowout Blast is Available Now!  https://goo.gl/4BTxnQ

#Nintendo3DS #KirbysBlowoutBlast
